                        <bindingDesc>
                            <binding contemporary="false">
                                <p>Early modern binding. Brown leather over wooden boards. 5 double raised bands and endbands. 2 hooked clasps with small, etched ornamental patterns. Blind-stamped on <locus from="LCO" to="LCO" scheme="other"/>: the letters <quote>I S D E</quote>, and below, <quote>1614</quote>. <locus from="Spine" to="Spine" scheme="other"/>: a paper label with the signum <quote>324</quote>; below, stamped in gold: the current signum, <quote>A 183</quote>. Below, remnants of a paper label.</p>
                                <p>
