                                        <width quantity="120" unit="mm"/>
                                        <depth quantity="56" unit="mm"/>
                                    </dimensions>
                                </p>
                                <decoNote type="tooling">
                                    <p>A medallion on the <locus from="LCO" to="LCO" scheme="other"/> and <locus from="RCO" to="RCO" scheme="other"/>, outlined by a gilt laurel wreath; the rest of the motif worn off. A centre panel surrounded by a triple-outlined frame containing floral patterns. A flower in the corner of each centre panel.</p>
                                </decoNote>
