                                        <measure type="textblockLeaves" quantity="240" unit="folios"/>
                                    </extent>
                                    <condition>The edges have been trimmed with loss of some of the text of the marginal notations. The two bifolia making up <locus from="138" to="138" scheme="folios"/>/ <locus from="141" to="141" scheme="folios"/> and <locus from="139" to="139" scheme="folios"/> / <locus from="140" to="140" scheme="folios"/> respectively have been placed in the wrong order and should switch places. <!--A dummy-quire of 12 leaves has been inserted after f. 240v for support.--></condition>
